name: Aubrey Dress
description: How amazing is our Aubrey dress? We are loving the lace detail which gives it the perfect touch of sophistication.

name: The Kyle Cardigan
description:
Not only is this a great cardigan to stay warm during the holidays, but also has a rich hunter green floral paisley print. It's a knit sweater boho chic style duster long cardigan.
99% Polyester, 1% Spandex. Made in USA.

name: The Chelsea Dress
description: Our gorgeous sleeveless and fitted cocktail mini dress has a shiny studded front and back design for an alluring look.

name: Liza Dress
description: This little black dress feautures a plunging neckline and keyhole style open back. Comes with a gold link chain belt to give it that extra touch!

name: Heather Top
description: Stunner alert! This gorgeous lace crochet top is to die for and so chic! Features a delicate keyhole on the back to finish it off with perfection.

name: Cindy Jumper
description: This soft and unique jumper is great for any occasion but even better for the holidays! Features a cage back, adjustable straps and pockets. Add accessories for a complete and effortless look.

name: Leopard Love Skirt
description: Adorable and chic leopard print mini skirt featuring an asymmetrical hem and zipper.

name: Petunia Black Top
description: It's all in the details! This gorgeous top features a crystal beading neckline that gives it that extra touch of delicacy and is finished off with a modest keyhole on the back.

name: Petunia Fuchsia Top
description: It's all in the details! This gorgeous top features a crystal beading neckline that gives it that extra touch of delicacy and is finished off with a modest keyhole on the back.

name: Black Sequin Pants
description: Black sequin and lace tuxedo style pants. These beauties feature a delicate and chic lace fabric and have a detailed tuxedo style solid black strip on each side. They have a drawstring waist to accomidate your waist line.

name: Fringe Kimono
description: Stunning white lace kimono with detail fringing on the hemline.

name: Scarf Print Jacket
description: Fun and oh so trendy is this chic chiffon scarf print jacket.

name: Jagged Mini Skirt
description: Biker chic? This unique faux leather mini has a jagget cut hem line with a python trim detail. Pair it with combat boots for an edgy look or keep it chic with a blouse and pumps. However you choose to wear it, you'll be sure to get a compliment!

name: Knit Sweater
description: A perfect combination of comft and style. This sweater is light-weight and has a loose weaving which allows it to be "stretchy" yet form fitting.

name: Sequin Collar Blouse
description: Add a little sparkle to your closet this season with this gorgeous sequin collar blouse. The perfect combination of black and gold.

name: Blushing Aztec Leggings
description: Super soft, gorgeous design and hard to ignore! The blushing aztec leggings are perfect for a day to night look and will keep you warm during these cool Fall nights. These leggings are available in one size fits most.

name: The Tahl Dress
description: Sophistication at it's best! This gorgeous yet sexy dress includes mesh fabric in the mid region and is finished off with a keyhole on the back.

name: Texture Me Leggings
description: Super soft printed leggings in a gorgeous print fabric with an array of colors that gives them a fabulous yet unique look. One size fits most!

name: Chelsea Gold Jacket
description: The Chelsea Gold Jacket is simply stunning and features zipper pockets and ribbing. The gold thread creates a brocade like print all over the jacket.

name: Geo Wrap Dress
description: The GEO wrap dress is a gorgeous silky and slinky wrap dress which ties at the waist.

name: Beige Cold Shoulder Sweater Dress
description:
Adorable and chic!
This dress is simple yet has it all with cold shoulder sleeves and adjustable tie straps.

name: Blue Cold Shoulder Sweater Dress
description:
Adorable and chic!
This dress is simple yet has it all with cold shoulder sleeves and adjustable tie straps.

name: Paisley Dress
description: Sleek and chic orange brocade dress with open cut out back. The dress is double lined and has a perfect fit!

name: Batwing Dress
description: This chic multi-color print dress is a show stopper! Wear it loose or accessorize it with a skinny belt. This dress features batwing sleeves and has a tie-up back.

name: Laser Cut MiniSkirt
description: Sport this flirty meets chic skirt for an edgy spin on a super feminine look. This faux leather skirt features small laser cut-outs for a unique design in the front and features a solid back. The upper panel has organic laser cut-outs contrasted against uniform square perforations on the bottom. Skirt is finished with a side invisible zipper.

name: Jessie Top
description: This off the shoulder Jessie top can be work short sleeve or long sleeve. Feautures a beautiful bold print.

name: Black & White Blouse
description: Black and white square print blouse has a touch of class yet edgy look. This gorgeous button down top has a detailed button on the arm to allow you to roll up and wear it as a quarter sleeve.

name: Printed Dress
description:
Great summer dress! Breezy and flowy for a trendy look.
This dress is available as a ONE SIZE, however, fits a small & medium.

Only available in red.

name: High Wasted High/Low
description: Exclusive design by Veronica Burgueno for VB Designs. This one of a kind garment is double lined with a unique hand painted butterfly print design by Arianne for Ramona LaRue.

name: Chief Sweater
description: Trendy yet comfortable over-sized sweater with indian print.

name: Palazzo Pants
description: Amazing 100% Indian silk palazzo pants with rouched elastic waistband. Lightweight and so comfy for a hot summer day.

name: Lace Tank Top
description: Sophistication is the best way to describe this lace scalloped tank. Layer it with tone on tone color or be your own trendsetter and pair it with a bold summer color.

name: Triangle Necklace
description: Stunner 14k gold-plated necklace features amethyst crystals inlay at the geometric details. Adjustable length and lobster-claw clasp.

name: Shoulder Dress
description: One shoulder solid knit jersey dress with short sleeve is unlined and light weight. Great for these hot summer days.

name: Wrap Around Bracelet
description: Gold plated chain, black crystal, gray tone cotton braided multi-strand wrap bracelet. 12.5 inch.

name: Wrap Bracelet
description: Wear it alone or stack 'em up! Dark gray tone cotton thread and gold plated chain braided wrap bracelet. 6.5 - 8 inch adjustable.

name: Heart Shape Knuckle Ring
description: 18k gold plated heart dainty or knuckle ring. One size and sure to dress up your finger with a sophisticated edge.

name: Pink Embellished Dress
description: Sure to be a head turner! This vibrant pink mini has embellishment down the front and along the shoulders.

name: Lace Trim Shorts
description: Look luscious and sweet this season with a little lace. These gorgeous floral shorts are the perfect way to go from casual to a glam evening look.

name: Silk Cuff Shorts
description: One of a kind design by Veronica Burgueno for VB Designs. These exquisite lined silk cuff shorts are sure to be a head turner.
